description:
This week, I'm reacting to Ingrid Andress and her recent performance of the "Star-Spangled Banner" at the Home Run Derby. There were a lot of negative headlines  - even after she explained the reasons behind it. Were any of them deserved?  

For Behind The Scenes footage, tips on ball skills or to talk to me in a monthly Zoom Chat Night, head over to my Patreon: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk
